Windows 10 - VirusTotal Integration
Windows 10 Setup
Windows 10 is used as an endpoint system in the SOC Lab environment. It generates Windows security events and user activities that can be 
investigated during security monitoring and incident response activities.
________________________________________
VirusTotal Integration
VirusTotal is used as a threat intelligence platform to analyze suspicious files, URLs, IP addresses, domains, and file hashes. During investigations,
suspicious indicators can be checked against VirusTotal's database to determine whether they are malicious or associated with known threats.
Website:
https://www.virustotal.com/
________________________________________
How It Helps in This Project
•	Analyze suspicious files and file hashes
•	Check malicious URLs and domains
•	Verify suspicious IP addresses
•	Enrich security alerts with threat intelligence
•	Support incident investigation and threat hunting
•	Improve decision-making during alert analysis
________________________________________
Investigation Workflow
Security Alert
       ↓
SOC Analyst Investigation
       ↓
Extract File Hash / IP / URL
       ↓
VirusTotal Lookup
       ↓
Threat Intelligence Results
       ↓
